            "text": "Here are some of the highly-rated options for chemical peel facials in Katy, TX, based on the search results:\n\n*   **H-Town Aesthetics:** Offers VI Chemical Peels, known for improving skin tone and texture, reducing signs of aging, and diminishing scarring. They offer a range of specialized treatments like VI Peel Original, Advanced, Precision Plus, and Purify, each targeting specific skin concerns. A Tox Booster Chemical Peel is also available to enhance the effects of VI Peels by targeting fine lines and wrinkles.\n*   **Anita's Skin Care Clinic:** This clinic provides custom facials and chemical peels, taking a holistic approach to skincare to address individual skin concerns.\n*   **Viata Aesthetics and Wellness:** Provides chemical peels tailored to your unique skin needs. They offer Vi Peels and Vi Peel Precision Plus, which can improve skin tone, texture, and clarity, fade sunspots, and soften lines and wrinkles.\n*   **Face to Face Spa:** This medical spa offers chemical peels to support renewed smoothness, as well as other advanced options. They offer a wide array of skincare services in addition to chemical peels, and a series of six progressive exfoliation treatments spaced two weeks apart is typically recommended for optimal improvement.\n*   **Luxe Medical Aesthetics:** Combines cutting-edge techniques and professional care with high-quality medical-grade products.\n*   **Luminous MediSpa Katy:** This med spa combines the relaxing aspects of a traditional spa with medical-grade treatments.\n*   **AVIVA Dermatology:** Expert dermatologists provide personalized chemical peel treatments to rejuvenate your skin.\n\nWhen choosing a location, consider the specific skin concerns you want to address, the type of peel offered, and the experience and qualifications of the staff.\n"
          }
